reviewText: Love Scooby and this dvd is great.
Goes with my set.  There are some shows on other sets. I kept it.
this is a great collection of Scooby-doo episodes. it is fun and enjoyable to watch. if you have not seen this dvd then I recommend you do

This DVD features all the episodes which were used as inspiration for the new Scooby Doo Lego Sets. Two new-to-DVD episodes.

Episodes on this disk are:

  Scooby-Doo and a Mummy, Too!
  The Headless Horseman of Halloween
  Which Witch is Which
  Fright House of a Lighthouse
  What A Night For A Knight!
  Hassle In The Castle
  A Gaggle of Galloping Ghosts
  Scoo-Be Or Not Scoo-Be
